                    <h5 className="font-bold text-teal-800 mb-2 uppercase text-xs sm:text-sm border-l-4 border-teal-600 pl-2">I. Tr·∫°ng Th√°i Ch·∫≠u</h5>
                    <div className="overflow-hidden border border-gray-400 rounded">
                        <table className="w-full text-[10px] sm:text-sm border-collapse">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
